<p class=MsoNormal><u><font size=3 face=TimesNewRomanPSMT><span
style='font-size:12.0pt'>And, if I run &#8216;lamboot&#8217;, it works !<o:p></o:p></span></font></u></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><b><font size=3 face=TimesNewRomanPSMT><span
